{
  "stem": "10162.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the summer of 1956, I decided to get a divorce because the children were two and three, and I just didn't want them to grow up and to be old enough to hear this, this man who, who would come home at the wee hours of the, the night and, and, and go into a rage and break furniture.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I want to jump out of the window and go to jump in the Danube.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this went on all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I got a divorce, and-- which didn't quite end it, because he kept coming back and saying, you know, saying that he will change and all that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, in 1956, October, which was two months after my divorce, the Hungarian revolution broke out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I did have some part in the revolution because I used to go to these clandestine meetings.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I wasn't an anti-communist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I was an anti-Stalinist, an ant-- anti-totalitarian form of, of communism.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I certainly wasn't for, for imperialism or, or the country being run over by any, any other superpower.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I just had enough of all this, and I, I wanted justice.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was going to these meetings.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't do anything more heroic than that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that's what-- that's what everybody did who was in my situation until, suddenly, the, the atmosphere was such that it was really enough to lit that legendary match and the whole thing would explode.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody thought that, that anything could happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then when the Hungarian revolution just erupted.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the children were, by the divorce process, given to me anyway.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I grabbed the two children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I went out, and I left the country, went to Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
